        'meta_title' => 'Subic and Zambales Two-Day Plan | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A calm two-day plan combining Subic Freeport attractions with the Zambales coves and Liwliwa surf, with bus options, food picks, and what to bring.',
