        'meta_title' => 'Kamay ni Hesus Shrine and Lucban Half-Day | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A calm half-day plan from Manila to Kamay ni Hesus Shrine in Lucban, Quezon, paired with a town heritage walk and pancit habhab lunch.',
